Package: wbes.dashboard
Title: World Bank Enterprise Surveys - Business Environment Benchmarking Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jean Victor", "Kwizera", , "info@kwizresearch.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Enterprise-grade Shiny dashboard for analyzing and benchmarking 
    business environments across 168 economies using World Bank Enterprise Survey 
    data. Built on the Appsilon Rhino framework following software development 
    best practices including modular architecture, comprehensive testing, and 
    reproducible data quality documentation.
